    <title>手动获取AOI教程</title>
    <link href="/2023/10/22/%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%A8%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96AOI%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <url>/2023/10/22/%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%A8%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96AOI%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>因为高德存在反爬取机制，难以批量获得我们需要的面状要素，所以我们通过获取当你点击地图中要素时这个面信息的响应来挑选出构成面的点集和属性字段。</p><h2 id="响应获取"><a href="#响应获取" class="headerlink" title="响应获取"></a>响应获取</h2><p>首先我们拿出爬取的徐州市综合医院excel表，下载火狐浏览器（必须），打开高德地图，按下f12打开开发者模式，选择网络。</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/22/CFkORIHmUyDs7uS.png" alt="image-20231022235149603"></p><p>在搜索框中搜索detail，复制响应信息</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/22/qm4Mgj791ZEBIdt.png" alt="image-20231022235434634"></p><p>新建一个txt文件，将响应的数据复制进来，并修改文件名称为id后面的字符串，这个是AOI数据的名称</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/22/qIBa837jU2idoM5.png" alt="image-20231022235630993"></p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/23/Eci23rDMjvlJ54A.png" alt="image-20231023000024612"></p><p>以上是准备工作</p><h2 id="Python处理JSON数据"><a href="#Python处理JSON数据" class="headerlink" title="Python处理JSON数据"></a>Python处理JSON数据</h2><p>这段代码能够处理你路径下的txt文件，生成一个新的txt，复制新的txt内容，粘贴至一个新的excel中</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs Python">root = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;D:/CUMT/项目/WebGIS医院停车场检测/AOI爬取/XZ_3jia/&quot;</span>      <span class="hljs-comment">#修改为你自己的路径</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> os, json<br><br>fs = os.listdir(root)<br>keys = []<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> f <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> fs:<br>    t = <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(root + f, encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;utf8&#x27;</span>).read()<br>    js = json.loads(t)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> k <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> js[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;data&#x27;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;base&#x27;</span>].keys():<br>        keys.append(k)<br><br>keys = <span class="hljs-built_in">list</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">set</span>(keys))<br>keys.sort()<br><br>ex = [<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;alias_name&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;brand_code&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;geodata&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;importance_vip_flag&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;checked&#x27;</span>]<br>output = <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Base1.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;wb&#x27;</span>)<br>title = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t&#x27;</span>.join(keys) + <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span><br>output.write(title.encode(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;utf8&#x27;</span>))<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> f <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> fs:<br>    t = <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(root + f, encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;utf8&#x27;</span>).read()<br>    js = json.loads(t)<br>    c = []<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> k <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> keys:<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span>:<br>            c.append(<span class="hljs-built_in">str</span>(js[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;data&#x27;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;base&#x27;</span>][k]))<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">except</span>:<br>            c.append(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;EMPTY&#x27;</span>)<br>    out = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t&#x27;</span>.join(c) + <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span><br>    output.write(out.encode(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;utf8&#x27;</span>))<br>output.close()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/23/kV4FdYNTrf1uzH7.png" alt="image-20231023001634505"></p><p>接下来获取点集数据</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python">output_2 = <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Points.txt&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;wb&#x27;</span>)<br>title = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;x\ty\tpoiid\n&#x27;</span><br>output_2.write(title.encode(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;utf8&#x27;</span>))<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> f <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> fs:<br>    t = <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(root + f, encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;utf8&#x27;</span>).read()<br>    js = json.loads(t)<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">try</span>:<br>        poiid = js[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;data&#x27;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;base&#x27;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;poiid&#x27;</span>]<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">len</span>(js[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;data&#x27;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;spec&#x27;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;mining_shape&#x27;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;shape&#x27;</span>]) &gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>:<br>            pts = js[<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;data&#x27;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;spec&#x27;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;mining_shape&#x27;</span>][<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;shape&#x27;</span>].split(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;;&#x27;</span>)<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> pt <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> pts[:-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]:<br>                x, y = pt.split(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;,&#x27;</span>)<br>                out = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#123;0&#125;\t&#123;1&#125;\t\n&#x27;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(x, y)<br>                output_2.write(out.encode(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;utf8&#x27;</span>))<br>            x, y = pts[-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>].split(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;,&#x27;</span>)<br>            out = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#123;0&#125;\t&#123;1&#125;\t&#123;2&#125;\n&#x27;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(x, y, poiid)<br>            output_2.write(out.encode(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;utf8&#x27;</span>))<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">except</span> Exception <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> e:<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">repr</span>(e))<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">print</span>(f)<br><br>output_2.close()<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行上述代码能获得一个Points.txt的点集文件</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/23/8jGidEg4zNYSc2J.png" alt="image-20231023002133369"></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> os,shapefile <span class="hljs-comment">#安装pyshp模块 pip install pyshp</span><br>root = os.getcwd() +<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> txt <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> os.listdir(root):<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> txt[-<span class="hljs-number">4</span>:] == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;.txt&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Points&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> txt:<br>        rd = shapefile.Writer(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#123;0&#125;.shp&#x27;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(txt.replace(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;.txt&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>)),shapeType=<span class="hljs-number">5</span>)<br>        rd.field(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;poiid&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;C&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;15&#x27;</span>)<br><br>        f = <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(root+txt).read().splitlines()[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>:]<br>        pt = []<br>        poly = []<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> f:<br>            pt = [<span class="hljs-built_in">float</span>(i.split(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t&#x27;</span>)[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]),<span class="hljs-built_in">float</span>(i.split(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t&#x27;</span>)[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>])]<br>            poly.append(pt)<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> i.split(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t&#x27;</span>)[<span class="hljs-number">2</span>] != <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>:<br>               fc1 = i.split(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\t&#x27;</span>)[<span class="hljs-number">2</span>]<br>               rd.record(fc1)<br>               <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> poly[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] != poly[-<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]:<br>                    poly.append(poly[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>])<br>               rd.poly([poly])<br>               poly = []<br>        rd.close()<br><br>        wgs84 = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;GEOGCS[&quot;GCS_WGS_1984&quot;,DATUM[&quot;D_WGS_1984&quot;,SPHEROID[&quot;WGS_1984&quot;,6378137.0,298.257223563]],PRIMEM[&quot;Greenwich&quot;,0.0],UNIT[&quot;Degree&quot;,0.0174532925199433]]&#x27;</span><br>        prj = <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#123;0&#125;.prj&#x27;</span>.<span class="hljs-built_in">format</span>(txt.replace(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;.txt&#x27;</span>,<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>)),<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;wb&#x27;</span>)<br>        prj.write(wgs84.encode(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;utf8&#x27;</span>))<br>        prj.close()<br><span class="hljs-built_in">input</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;点要素转面完毕，按任意键退出！&#x27;</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行上述文件会获得shp文件，在arcgis中需要选择修复几何进行处理。</p><p>但是这是高德GCJ02坐标系，需要转换为WGS84坐标系。</p><p>在ArcGIS中打开，并链接到之前保存的excel表，链接字段为poiid。</p><p><img src="https://s2.loli.net/2023/10/23/sXC3nGKEglprNIy.png" alt="image-20231023100056098"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
